{"id":"283ee385-0620-46e7-a56d-5885c89dd3be","name":"Still in Love (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><em>Veiled Rose<br>スティルインラブ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧･ﾟ:* 🌹 *:･ﾟ✧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/u_3px46IkNo742kGgNXpY.webp\" style=\"width: 531px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ: 🌹 :･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><em>At first glance, Still in Love seems to be a quiet and sensible Umamusume with only a fondness of sweets to make her distinguishable from others. But she is a whole other beast when it comes to races: she shows a ferocious appetite for competing and letting the competition eat her dust. Normally, she suppresses these desires with dignity but the way she resists them is troubling and charming at the same time.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><br><em>\"My name is Still in Love. I... I'm not worthy of any more introduction... I like to... keep those things to myself...”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/10eUjAenXuqsj11fP0YV4.webp\" style=\"width: 463px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ: 🌹 :･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><br><em>1) First meeting</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><em>2) Jealousy</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><em>3) Coffee &amp; Sweets</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><em>4) Winning the Triple Tiara</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><em>5) The reunion</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 14, 14);\"><strong><em>6) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/AGUTfyvB9oX-J3zvfjAsP.webp\" style=\"width: 411px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ: 🌹 :･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">5 scenarios, enjoy.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/szNgd9bLz61xd3WejT6q5.webp\" style=\"width: 577px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✧･ﾟ:✧･ﾟ: ✧･ﾟ: 🌹 :･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧:･ﾟ✧</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/CoconToozai/status/1954033143956275212/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">CoconToozai (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/UmaMusume/comments/1ma6bm7/still_in_love_before_the_race_by_%E3%81%8F%E3%82%89%E3%81%86%E3%81%A1%E3%82%93%E3%81%90%E3%82%B9%E3%82%BF%E3%83%BC%E3%83%88/\" target=\"_blank\">2nd art TL source</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/122631851\" target=\"_blank\">2nd art original source (Pixiv)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/A4_EiSHi/status/1960086198619386171\" target=\"_blank\">@A4_Eishi</a></p><p style=\"text